description: The Bratwurst King is a mobile food unit serving a variety of delicious European style sausages and other unique food products. We provide one of a kind meal experience and are unique to the Washington DC area. We aim to create or bring back great memories about traditional European cuisine. Regardless if you have already been to Germany or Austria and enjoyed a quick hot meal at the local "Bratwurst Stand" or are trying our products for the first time, we are sure that your experience will be a pleasant one.Our suppliers have been carefully selected thus guaranteeing the most authentic ingredients in all our offerings. All meals are prepared with a passion for perfection. Our attention to detail combined with our experience ensures a tasty and enjoyable experience time after time.
name: The Bratwurst King
